    <abstract>
      <t>   This document describes a REST API that supports the normative
   requirements of the SCITT Architecture.  Optional key discovery and
   query interfaces are provided to support interoperability issues with
   Decentralized Identifiers, X509 Certificates and Artifact
   Repositories.

